cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR

The paper discusses techniques for authenticating audiovisual recordings, which involves aspects of computer security (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of private and public information also suggests a potential connection to cryptography (cs.CR).
